						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying near a field called Bhāvichēnu 2 km to the West of the village.</p>						

						<p>This undated inscription may be assigned to the 15th century, on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. It states the field belonged to god Virūpākshadēva of Diguvapaṭnam.</p>						

						</summary>
